[Para. (fA) inserted by s. 6 of Act 9/93]

(g)     that every person who is to be an executive officer of the proposed bank has sufficient experience of the management
of the kind of business it is intended to conduct;
[Para. (g) amended by s. 6 of Act 22/2013]

